%%{init: {'theme': 'base', 'themeVariables': {'lineColor': '#ffffff', 'edgeLabelBackground': '#ffffff'}}}%%
flowchart TD
    classDef good fill:#00B894,stroke:#00A381,color:#fff,font-weight:bold
    classDef bad  fill:#E17055,stroke:#C0392B,color:#fff,font-weight:bold
    classDef info fill:#0984E3,stroke:#2980B9,color:#fff,font-weight:bold
    classDef warn fill:#FDCB6E,stroke:#E17055,color:#2D3436,font-weight:bold
    classDef decision fill:#DFE6E9,stroke:#636E72,color:#2D3436,font-weight:bold

    A(["`**NEW EVENT ARRIVES**
    Inngest creates a fresh run.
    No step cache exists yet.`"]):::info

    B{"`**Step 1 completed
    in this run before?**`"}:::decision

    C["`**EXECUTE step code fresh**
    Calls Gemini and Qdrant.
    Gets real results.`"]:::good

    D["`**Cache step 1 result**
    RAGSearchResult stored under
    this run ID + step name.`"]:::good

    E["`**SKIP step code entirely**
    Returns old cached result.
    Your code fix has NO effect.`"]:::bad

    F{"`**Step 2 completed
    in this run before?**`"}:::decision

    G["`**EXECUTE step code fresh**
    Runs generate-answer normally.`"]:::good

    H["`**SKIP step code entirely**
    Returns old cached answer.`"]:::bad

    I(["`**Function returns final result**`"]):::info

    W["`**TRAP — Why retries fail after a bug fix:**
    Fix code → retry same run →
    Inngest still replays cached empty result.
    SOLUTION: Send a BRAND NEW event.`"]:::warn

    A ==> B
    B ==>|"No — first time"| C ==> D ==> F
    B ==>|"Yes — retry/replay"| E ==> F
    F ==>|"No — first time"| G ==> I
    F ==>|"Yes — retry/replay"| H ==> I
    E -.->|"causes this"| W
    H -.->|"causes this"| W

    linkStyle default stroke:#ffffff,stroke-width:2.5px
